{"tid":2121664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個屋企藍黃勢力分佈","createTime":"2020-07-23T12:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T14:16:00.000Z","uid":232585,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"691eee646f800d8f7eccb303d9f338317e3e47dc","tid":2121664,"uid":232585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"屋企得老豆我同母親大人三個<br />\n老豆係一個通情達理講道理嘅人<br />\n老母係典型藍，歪曲事實吹水唔抹咀 以為個世界圍撚住佢轉 etc.<br />\n<br />\n咁母親大人成日睇埋晒啲藍屍group信以為真<br />\n前一排食飯咁佢就開咗個題啦：<br />\n母親大人：最近睇咗篇野話原來肺炎開頭其實係美國嗰邊傳出嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：係囉美國正仆街中國又然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁篇嘢講咩嫁<br />\n母親大人：原來上年美軍整啲病毒去武漢，所以之後先爆得咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆：照你咁講都係叫武漢肺炎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n母親大人：唔係呀，係因為美國政府一早有心搞中國，美國欠中國一個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：大佬唔好痴線啦，先唔講篇野真唔真，一定係美國同隻病毒傾好咗只係搞中國唔搞美國啦，我喺美國就做定隻疫苗 大爆發之後掉隻疫苗出嚟做救世主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆：啱喎 而且美國都因為武漢肺炎跌咗唔少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n母親大人：errrrrrrrr&hellip;<br />\n跟住佢就開始講啲美國搞中國，特朗普點點點乜乜柒柒<br />\n就快針到佢一幢都冇嗰陣<br />\n母親大人：你睇吓佢(我)咩態度 就係因為你(老豆)教到佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我／老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就end topic次次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n真係人一藍腦便殘<br />\n呢啲性格係日常生活都會體驗得到<br />\n例如佢有糖尿，我同老豆叫佢戒口注重下健康<br />\n佢就話有藥食所以可以飲可樂<br />\n勸多佢幾句又嬲鳩，跟住係啲親戚面前話自己點慘妖魔化我哋兩個<br />\n好心當狗吠 到時出事咪又係搞著其他人<br />\n我真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還好有老豆幫手平衡下心理<br />\n恕我見識少真係想像唔到全家藍會係點"},{"pid":"abf108c50b97087c2f86b74a4e009ee067371abc","tid":2121664,"uid":291199,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"屋企三個人<br />\n兩個都係深紅冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ab2da8a91538b1ee675a0e535ac85f1d84c1fe","tid":2121664,"uid":209933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d256420926b49e833b002b47d4d9123712681cd","tid":2121664,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"老豆：藍<br />\n老母：深藍+紅"},{"pid":"250e4fbaee27a5e459d04a47e9dd2957241b9ee2","tid":2121664,"uid":44007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"兩老係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過老豆冷氣軍師 上年講親發夢就無影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912995700bc8c333b57f84cc1c7d3a0cd1ead6d5","tid":2121664,"uid":232585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"我諗我如果真係受佢教依個post應該起babycomdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ebba61702cda447c97a13ff2f38b1ee9a4c47f","tid":2121664,"uid":166405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d256420926b49e833b002b47d4d9123712681cd","tid":2121664,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"老豆：藍<br />\n老母：深藍+紅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"手足平時一定好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4d40a1d359deeadf0e8c9c7d35606d28b6cdfa","tid":2121664,"uid":83602,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"老母藍 <br />\n老豆大中華膠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /