":"手足平時一定好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"咁又唔會嘅 政治啲嘢就少講囉<br />\n不過我有時會扮紅串鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如 每日新增勁多確診 <br />\n我：多謝林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，多謝習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ed5607e07dee684094efc47c0712b60a104586","tid":2121664,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"老豆深紅<br />\n老母淺黃<br />\n呀哥淺黃<br />\n我深黃"},{"pid":"cf81d80310b6bffd22ade17711d1841c037a0a99","tid":2121664,"uid":232585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1ab2da8a91538b1ee675a0e535ac85f1d84c1fe","tid":2121664,"uid":209933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"大家都係有理說不清<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b560719d211e699b3653888a72992f4c1a981a","tid":2121664,"uid":64538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"老豆：深藍<br />\n成日播埋佢啲fd sd比佢嘅藍絲片<br />\n<br />\n老母：中立撚/港豬<br />\n知道班後生爭取啲乜，但武肺呢單里全世界都屌緊政府，佢就覺得政府冇做錯"},{"pid":"62dfca9bd18e0c199dd1f1696ec42e292bdab825","tid":2121664,"uid":232585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e39088b5b87ea03bf4ec3bd252812c31d91870ae","tid":2121664,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32ebba61702cda447c97a13ff2f38b1ee9a4c47f","tid":2121664,"uid":166405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d256420926b49e833b002b47d4d9123712681cd","tid":2121664,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:44:14.000Z","msg":"老豆：藍<br />\n老母：深藍+紅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"手足平時一定好寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\